# Cursor Rule: style

## Language
- TypeScript strict mode.
- ESLint + Prettier; no stylistic overrides in files.

## Naming
- Functions: verbNoun
- Booleans: is/has/should
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE for env-only, otherwise camelCase.

## UI Style (if React)
- Functional components.
- Hooks > classes.
- Tailwind or CSS Modules; no inline styles except dynamic one-offs.

## Docs
- JSDoc/TSDoc for exported functions/components.
